## ðŸ“¦ Installation Options

### Standard Installation (SQLite only)
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### With MongoDB Support (for cloud deployment)
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
pip install pymongo dnspython
```

Or create `requirements-mongodb.txt`:
```txt
-r requirements.txt
pymongo>=4.6.0
dnspython>=2.4.0
```

Then install:
```bash
pip install -r requirements-mongodb.txt
```
